<br />

<br />
Well onto my question.  I read in the hunting guide many people suggested Cobalt Scar as a good zone to solo in.  Mostly wyverns.  Since those are all from 2002 I was wondering if this is still true.  If not can any one suggest a good zone?
<br />

<br />
(As far as my problems swarming:  First I dont know many of the zones well enough to get into a safe area.  Secondly I have never been able to get the mobs bunched up enough to all go for the pet.)</span></td>
