				<td colspan="2"><span>While in JP, try to swarm the Pottameids if the poachers are taken, they are snare immune and root immune so people rarely bother with them.
<br />

<br />
They are fairly slow, hit somewhat harder then poachers and proc some dd's.
<br />

<br />
Guardians are immune to fire dot, Maidens are immune to Charm, named are immune to charm and drop some stuff for quested Karana Weapons and druidic gear.
<br />
Easy to swarm on the open grassy field at the far end of the river, opposite direction from the poachers.
<br />

<br />
Not that good for cash drops, they used to drop gems but no longer seem to do so, but ok for xp.
<br />
At 56 about 1/3 of the mobs are still dblue, the rest is lblue so...<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
